lead_paragraph: Chinese wild-card entry Zhang Shuai opened the WTA Elite Trophy tournament with a 6-1, 6-1 win over sixth-seeded Timea Bacsinzky on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Zhang, Svitolina Win Opening Matches at WTA Elite Trophy
